README

Work in progress.

Cristin code still to be added and Duo-DSpace folder on github reorganised to just contain
duo module - currently duplicate code

---

duo folder to be copied to dspace/modules/
pom.xml to overwrite dspace/modules/pom.xml or insert additional profile into 
dspace/modules/pom.xml:

        <profile>
            <id>duo</id>
            <activation>
                <activeByDefault>true</activeByDefault>
            </activation>
            <modules>
                <module>duo</module>
            </modules>
        </profile>

---

The script will run the following commands


student-web.cfg
---------------
copy from dspace/modules/duo/config/student-web.cfg
to dspace/config/modules/student-web.cfg

swordv2-server.cfg
------------------
copy from dspace/modules/duo/config/swordv2-server.cfg
to dspace/config/modules/swordv2-server.cfg

dspace.cfg
----------
append dspace/modules/duo/config/dspace.cfg
to dspace/config/dspace.cfg

input-forms.xml
---------------
copy from dspace/modules/duo/config/input-forms.xml
to dspace/config/input-forms.xml

fs-submission.xsl
---------------
copy from dspace/modules/duo/config/crosswalks/fs-submission.xsl
to dspace/config/crosswalks/fs-submission.xsl

fs-metadata.xml
---------------
copy from dspace/modules/duo/config/registries/fs-metadata.xml
to dspace/config/registries/fs-metadata.xml

Import metadata
---------------
./dspace dsrun org.dspace.administer.MetadataImporter -f 
	dspace/modules/duo/config/registries/fs-metadata.xml

---

set up cron job
./dspace embargo-lifter 

